---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <main class="strategy-page">
    <section class="hero">
      <p class="eyebrow">Podcast Guest Strategy</p>
      <h1>100 Ranked Guests for We Scale Startups</h1>
      <p class="byline">Daniel Johnson | May 2026</p>
      <p class="lede">Warm leads · Authority builders · Hidden gems · Strategic partners</p>
      <nav aria-label="Page sections">
        <a href="#master-ranking">Master ranking</a>
        <a href="#invite-first">Invite first</a>
        <a href="#booking-plan">30-day plan</a>
        <a href="#templates">Outreach templates</a>
      </nav>
    </section>

    <section class="section-grid" aria-label="Strategy sections">
      <article><span>A</span><h2>Realistic Early Gets</h2><p>People already in Daniel's orbit or highly accessible cold reaches.</p></article>
      <article><span>B</span><h2>Authority Builders</h2><p>Higher difficulty guests who lift credibility and audience growth.</p></article>
      <article><span>C</span><h2>Hidden Gems</h2><p>Underexposed founders and operators with honest, useful stories.</p></article>
      <article><span>D</span><h2>Strategic Partners</h2><p>Guests who can open doors, build partnerships, or support WSS pipeline.</p></article>
    </section>

    <section id="master-ranking" class="content-block">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p class="eyebrow">Master Ranking</p>
        <h2>All 100 Guests</h2>
        <p>Ranked by overall priority: warm relationships, audience upside, and commercial potential for We Scale Startups.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="table-wrap">
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr><th>#</th><th>Name</th><th>Current Role</th><th>Suggested Episode Angle</th><th>Difficulty</th><th>Audience</th><th>Section</th></tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {guests.map(([rank, name, role, angle, difficulty, audience, section]) => (
              <tr>
                <td>{rank}</td>
                <td><strong>{name}</strong></td>
                <td>{role}</td>
                <td>{angle}</td>
                <td><span class={`pill ${String(difficulty).toLowerCase()}`}>{difficulty}</span></td>
                <td>{audience}</td>
                <td>{section}</td>
              </tr>
            ))}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="invite-first" class="content-block split">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Final Strategy Layer</p>
        <h2>The 15 Guests To Invite First</h2>
        <p>Lead with warm relationships. Record fast, publish fast, and use early clips to unlock harder guests.</p>
      </div>
      <ol class="rank-list">
        {firstInvites.map((name) => <li>{name}</li>)}
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="content-block two-col">
      <article>
        <h2>Most Likely To Create Inbound Consulting Leads</h2>
        <ul>{consultingLeads.map((name) => <li>{name}</li>)}</ul>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h2>Most Likely To Grow The Audience Fastest</h2>
        <ul>{audienceGrowth.map((name) => <li>{name}</li>)}</ul>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section id="booking-plan" class="content-block">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p class="eyebrow">Execution</p>
        <h2>30-Day Guest Booking Plan</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="plan-grid">
        {bookingPlan.map(([week, title, body]) => (
          <article>
            <span>{week}</span>
            <h3>{title}</h3>
            <p>{body}</p>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="templates" class="content-block">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p class="eyebrow">Outreach</p>
        <h2>Templates</h2>
        <p>Use these as starting points. Personalise every bracketed detail before sending.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="template-grid">
        {templates.map(([label, subject, body]) => (
          <article>
            <p class="template-label">{label}</p>
            {subject && <h3>{subject}</h3>}
            <p>{body}</p>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-block principles">
      <h2>Key Principles For Guest Booking Success</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Start warm, go cold with proof.</li>
        <li>Make it easy to say yes: no prep, 35-45 minutes, remote, recording provided.</li>
        <li>Reference their specific work in every pitch.</li>
        <li>Ask for referrals in every conversation.</li>
        <li>Build in public to create visible booking momentum.</li>
        <li>After 10 published episodes, use proof to lift pitch success rates.</li>
        <li>Protect the niche: operators and founders, not generic celebrity interviews.</li>
        <li>Use cross-promotion as the fastest growth channel.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="source-note">Built for Daniel Johnson and We Scale Startups, May 2026.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .strategy-page {
    background: #f7f4ee;
    color: #191917;
  }

  .hero,
  .content-block,
  .section-grid {
    width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 40px));
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero {
    min-height: 78vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 88px 0 56px;
  }

  .eyebrow,
  .byline,
  .template-label {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    color: #8c3d24;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h1,
  h2,
  h3,
  p {
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  h1 {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6.8rem);
    line-height: 0.94;
  }

  .lede {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 24px 0 28px;
    color: #4d4942;
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.45rem);
  }

  nav {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  nav a,
  .pill {
    border: 1px solid rgba(25, 25, 23, 0.18);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 9px 13px;
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: #fffdf8;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .section-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 0 0 46px;
  }

  .section-grid article,
  .content-block,
  .plan-grid article,
  .template-grid article,
  .two-col article {
    background: #fffdf8;
    border: 1px solid rgba(25, 25, 23, 0.12);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .section-grid article {
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .section-grid span {
    display: inline-grid;
    place-items: center;
    width: 34px;
    height: 34px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    background: #243c37;
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

